[NPC] Noxdar: You may not know it, but you have saved a life this day.
[NPC] Noxdar: I can't give you much, though.
[NPC] Noxdar: Perhaps this heart that I kept from my adventuring days?
[NPC] Noxdar: This armour?
[NPC] Noxdar: You decide.

